title: UN Demands Increased Humanitarian Aid to Pakistan, Afghanistan
text: More humanitarian aid is needed in Afghanistan and Pakistan, the director of the Operational Division at the UN Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) said after a visit to the two countries in the wake of the deadly attack on the Doctors Without Borders (MSF) hospital in Kunduz. ...
